Leslie Fernandez MM, Croix de Guerre, OBE - SOE trainer at Beaulieu and then F Section agent (two missions). He was also an Advisor on the film, ‘Carve her name with pride’.

This was based on the true story of Special Operations Executive agent Violette Szabo, GC, who was captured and executed while serving in Nazi-occupied France.

